                     <hi rend="largeCaps">ALICE McKENZIE</hi> (20)</persName>, was indicted<rs id="t18590509-477-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18590509-477-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
